Package: ecologyeffectsizeapp
Title: Ecological Effect Size Coding Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Multi-user R Shiny web application for systematic reviewers to
    extract, code, and standardise effect sizes from ecological primary literature.
    Supports multiple study designs (control/treatment, correlation, regression,
    interaction, time trend) with automated conversion to Pearson r and Fisher Z.
